{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "48af17a9-d7f4-4b5e-ad35-c577b75c5de2", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/48af17a9-d7f4-4b5e-ad35-c577b75c5de2@3.pkg/1772597567290/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597567475", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/48af17a9-d7f4-4b5e-ad35-c577b75c5de2@3.pkg/1772597567290/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597567475"}, "identifier": "48af17a9-d7f4-4b5e-ad35-c577b75c5de2", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>B：合宪性审查的核心目的是确保法律与宪法一致，从而维护宪法作为根本法的权威，故B符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>A：宪法具有最高法律地位，不需要提升了，故A说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>C：题干未提及对违宪行为的追责，而是强调立法前的预防性审查，故C不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>D：通过审查立法是否符合宪法，加强法律监督，能够推动宪法在实践中的落实，保障宪法实施是深层次原因，故D不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025湖南中考真题）全国人民代表大会及其常务委员会在每一个立法环节都把好宪法关，依法对所有提请审议的法律草案和决定决议草案进行合宪性审查，确保每一项立法都符合宪法精神。该做法旨在（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025湖南中考真题）全国人民代表大会及其常务委员会在每一个立法环节都把好宪法关，依法对所有提请审议的法律草案和决定决议草案进行合宪性审查，确保每一项立法都符合宪法精神。该做法旨在（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/48af17a9-d7f4-4b5e-ad35-c577b75c5de2@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754819449189", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": []